resources.string: ဝတ်မှုန်ရွှေရည်

\t\t\t\tWutt Hmone Shwe Yi started her acting with advertisements in 2009.She has made over 40 films.In 2013, Myanmar Times named her as one of the 50 Outstanding Myanmar Women.She also participated in Myanmar Famous Actor Pyay Ti Oo\'s Pyay Ti Oo Foundation Fund Raising Concert for students on December 4, 2011 and donated all her artist fees for the foundation.

\t\t\t\tHer relationship with singer/songwriter/actor Sai Sai Kham Leng was one of the most famous scandals dealing with celebrities. But they never made it to a public relationship and they broke up after some years.
